{"id": 6934, "title": "Ticket #6934: condor_ssh_to_job can't enter singularity container with older nsenter", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe code in the starter which allows an ssh_to_job user to enter a singularity container relies on the system utility nsenter.  Currently, the starter passes the -a flag to nsenter, to tell it to enter all the namespaces of the container.  Sadly, -a isn't supported on older Linux distributions, so let's explicitly list the namespaces we care about.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<strong>CODE REVIEW</strong>: Looks good.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Apr-08 19:14</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/140d82bc3cd93cf311c45e9e20c1f57b3eb13bd8\">[56528]</a></span>: Add version histoyr for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6934\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6934'); return false;\" title=\"condor_ssh_to_job can't enter singularity container with older nsenter\">#6934</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Feb-27 15:29</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/69300bbd37c6ec9e61180487390f72e77a5c7499\">[56253]</a></span>: Allow condor_ssh_to_job to singularity on older systems <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6934\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6934'); return false;\" title=\"condor_ssh_to_job can't enter singular